Localization.Name: Haruspec Goggles (Modified)
Localization.Description: This version of Stegman's Haruspec goggles has been modified from its original form. Supremely comfortable yet light as a feather, the Haruspec goggles also provide excellent protection against the elements thanks to their sturdy side shields. Stegman's fitted the goggles with polycarbonate performance lenses and a special slip-resistant nose pad to ensure they stay in place.
